---
title: Lamb Biryani with Tomato and Green Peas
description: Biryani, an Indian mixed rice dish, can be composed of a variety of meats, spices, herbs and vegetables. Our version uses ground lamb, sweet peas, tomatoes and a fragrant mix of spices, fresh mint and cilantro!
